Every day, our 98,000 employees around the world live out our commitment to better energy while relying on cutting-edge expertise that spans the entire energy chain. Not only are we oil and gas producers, refiners, distributors and petrochemical specialists, we are also the world’s second largest solar energy company. This global vision and interdisciplinary expertise allows us to work towards a responsible energy future.



Explore  and produceTo meet the energy needs of a burgeoning global population while preparing for the future, we continually innovate to produce sustainable and responsible solutions in oil and gas, solar energy, and bioenergies. 


Oil and GasDiscover 




SolarDiscover 




BioenergiesDiscover 

 



Transform  and develop You already know us through our network of service stations. But we do so much more to improve your daily life. Our industrial expertise in transforming oil and gas helps to produce a wide range of everyday items such as cars, packaging and household appliances. 


Refining - PetrochemicalsDiscover 




PolymersDiscover 




Specialty chemicalsDiscover 

 



Ship  and market We all require energy for heat, transportation, light in our homes and so much more. Total serves your needs worldwide each and every day. We bring energy from producing regions all the way to consumer hubs, working across a long, complex logistics chain. 


Trading and ShippingDiscover 




Products and ServicesDiscover 

 







 

