                Dividends              













 


 

 



Total’s dividend payment ensures that shareholders benefit from the growth of the company. Our dividend is proof of our commitment to long term value creation and with no dividend cut since 1982, it also offers an attractive yield. Here you can find the dividend dates, amounts and payment arrangements. 





 











 









 









 


